  "instructions": [
    "Shred the beetroot using a box grater and place it in a large bowl.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the apple cider vinegar, olive oil, maple syrup, Dijon mustard, and salt.",
    "Pour the vinaigrette over the beetroot and toss to coat.",
    "Cover the bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "Just before serving, sprinkle the chopped fresh dill over the top of the salad.",
    "Toss the salad gently to combine and serve chilled."
  ],
